TEXT.TITLE: CATTLE ON FEED REPORT CALLED NEGATIVE
TEXT.BODY: Chicago Mercantile Exchange floor traders' immediate comments on the 13-state USDA quarterly cattle on feed report were negative. Traders said that placements on feed and total on-feed numbers were at the high end of expectations and will likely weigh on futures tomorrow. Reuter
